Package: xournalpp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Handwritten note-taking supporting pen & PDF annotation
 Xournal++ is a GTK+ application for notetaking, sketching, annotating
 a PDF file, or keeping a journal. Supports Pen input like Wacom
 Tablets. Best used with a stylus, although usable with a mouse.
 Xournal++ is a reimplementation of the Xournal program, with an
 extended file format.
